President Donald Trump says “all is well.” The President of the United States responded to news of Iran attacking U.S. forces at Iraqi bases on Tuesday (January 7) with a tweet, according to JustJared. “All is well! Missiles launched from Iran at two military bases located in Iraq. Assessment of casualties & damages taking place now. So far, so good! We have the most powerful and well-equipped military anywhere in the world, by far! I will be making a statement tomorrow morning,” he said. Powered by RubiQube Ad Network 